        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2025-11",
        "text": "Maddy is an INCREDIBLE photographer. She photographed our wedding in June. She was an absolute joy to work with throughout the planning process, and really helped make sure our day went smoothly. She was consistently communicative and helpful. Even though we had never done a wedding before, it was incredibly helpful to have her, a wedding veteran and true professional, by our side. We also felt like she captured our day in a way that felt really authentic- when we look at the photos they really evoke a sense of feeling and place and memory, more than any other professional photos we have had done before. We cannot recommend her enough!!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2025-11",
        "text": "Maddy photographed my wedding last weekend. I have still only seen sneak peaks and I KNOW she slayed the rest. (The sneak peeks are a 10/10). Maddy did an amazing job keeping everyone on track for photos and honestly just keeping my whole night on track. She was more than just a photographer to me she was such a support. She helped me with my bustle and so much more. Do not walk, run to booking her for your wedding. I can't wait to see the rest of the photos. Thank you Maddy♡♡"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2024-12",
        "text": "Maddy is AMAZING!! We couldn’t have asked for a better photographer for our wedding day. She was such a pleasure to work with and captured our love perfectly. She also did not mind that my family and friends wanted to capture the day with their own cameras/phones. I highly recommend Maddy!!!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2025-09",
        "text": "Maddy is such a talented photographer, she spent our wedding day with us and her photos are absolutely stunning. For posed photos, she knew exactly where and how to set us up, and the candid photos she got of us, our friends, and family are perfect. I don’t know how she was able to catch all of these fleeting moments the exact second they were taking place. As a person, she is an absolute joy. You feel very comfortable and relaxed in her presence, she’s very fun and easy to talk to, and she cares about getting to know you. She goes above and beyond, I could not recommend her enough."
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2026-01",
        "text": "We loved working with Maddy for our engagement and wedding photos and can't recommend her enough! She is able to capture special moments in a natural way that did not feel like we were having our photos taken or we were being posed. Her digital and film shots are beautiful and I truly could not pick a favorite shot if I had to. Her calm, unflappable demeanor kept us at ease and we look forward to working with her for more life events in the future!"
      }
